        "endTime": 44841,
        "slowStartTime": 65016,
        "slowEndTime": 67486
    },
    {
        "text": "...I want to run a small firm that searches for the right candidate for clients.",
        "startTime": 45175,
        "endTime": 49569,
        "slowStartTime": 67912,
        "slowEndTime": 74579
    },
    {
        "text": "I guess after people retire, no need to say,...",
        "startTime": 50171,
        "endTime": 52639,
        "slowStartTime": 75406,
        "slowEndTime": 79183
    },
    {
        "text": "...most of them feel down in the dumps and depressed.",
        "startTime": 52963,
        "endTime": 55586,
        "slowStartTime": 79594,
        "slowEndTime": 83604
    },
    {
        "text": "Often they feel useless and like they contribute nothing to society...",
        "startTime": 56218,
        "endTime": 60650,
        "slowStartTime": 84477,
        "slowEndTime": 91200
    },
    {
        "text": "...and that all they do is sit at home.",
